592
00:29:53.787 --> 00:29:55.869
Do yourself a favor.

593
00:29:55.952 --> 00:29:57.289
Keep going.

594
00:30:07.636 --> 00:30:09.385
Get the boys together.

595
00:30:09.468 --> 00:30:11.090
DEPUTY DANN: Didn't Wyatt
