and do you know why?

605
00:30:45.542 --> 00:30:46.893
It's because of you.

606
00:30:46.976 --> 00:30:50.795
Because he is watching
you and what you do.

607
00:30:50.878 --> 00:30:52.464
Look. I lost it. all right?

608
00:30:52.547 --> 00:30:54.270
It's over.

609
00:30:54.353 --> 00:30:56.315
