-Yeah.

616
00:31:09.368 --> 00:31:10.824
And I meant what I said.

617
00:31:11.835 --> 00:31:14.201
BECCA: Yeah. I
remember that promise.

618
00:31:21.509 --> 00:31:22.913
Wine?

619
00:31:24.009 --> 00:31:26.663
It's not just any wine.

620
00:31:26.746 --> 00:31:29.238
