682
00:34:24.095 --> 00:34:26.746
Hon. I had too many
churros with my macchiato.

683
00:34:26.829 --> 00:34:28.474
I'll see you at the park.

684
00:34:28.557 --> 00:34:31.448
-BECCA: What? No.
-Have fun.

685
00:34:31.531 --> 00:34:34.086
