692
00:35:03.096 --> 00:35:04.513
-Vest?
-I'm good.

693
00:35:04.596 --> 00:35:05.953
-Excuse us. Oh. hi.
-Excuse us. Excuse us.

694
00:35:06.036 --> 00:35:07.551
-Yeah. yeah. Absolutely.
-Right up front?

695
00:35:07.634 --> 00:35:08.890
BOAT DRIVER: Just head
